trend_summary: Early imagery shows a wooded suburb with one large construction zone. Later scenes reveal a completed subdivision, extra commercial pads near the main road, minor street upgrades and modest infill housing. Overall built-up area grows moderately while central forest cover shrinks slightly but remains dominant.
notable_changes: Southeastern construction site transformed into a finished curvilinear housing subdivision.
New commercial/industrial buildings added along the southwest arterial road.
Incremental infill housing and garage additions within older western neighborhood blocks.
Tree canopy loss at forest edge and within new subdivision, though core woodland persists.
